column5: We are crossing thru pensaltucky now.Should be at Spiels aroud 4:00.Tomorrow.....Lakair!
Spiel has his apron on and boilin' up some crawdads to serve over the jambalaya.   See you Friday morning. I'll be driving in with the window open...pass me a cold one.
enjoy your time up their in paradise, cant wait for the stories and pics from this years event. have fun and be safe.  jason
Dang! Spiel better get his ass in gear, much to do....................

Safe travels everyone. I believe it was you Spiel that said it takes a week of packing and planning to getaway for a couple of days of fishing or something to that effect. You'd think that you'd have it all figured out by now. Having said that, I better get my:asshat: in gear and start packing as my trip is coming up in a week.

I had 52 weeks to get ready for this Will and I'm still frantically packing right now (okay I'm taking a breather, but I've more to do). I'd be a great procrastinator if I wasn't always putting it off.
Border patrol has been notified!!!  Have a fun time you guys and gals!!!
great... my property values have just dropped
The proper authorities will be dually notified.
HAHAHA Dually, is that because there are two of them?
Nah. He's driving the big pickup.  Hey y'all, have a ball. Wish I was goin'.  JF

Really looking forward to finally seeing you guys, Joe, I'll put you in charge of the pickled leeks, that way you can snag a few to take home to your wife. Wish I had more of them but I only have the one jar left so that will have to do!
We are at Chris's house enjoying a few pops with Fish Farmer and eating some Gumbo. Joe
Glad you made it safe and sound.  See you in two days!!  Joey

It was nice meeting you guys, and that Gumbo was great. Wish I was going with you. Like I have repeated many times, I've got to do the Lakeair trip one day. Just talking to you guys, I don't know if I'd bring my tackle, be nice just sitting around talking to everyone. I don't know if the body could handle it  Have a safe and enjoyable trip everyone. Can't wait to see the posts when yous get back.
